# Design Tokens & Styling

## Color Palette

Only three colors: green, white, black. No other colors allowed.

- `text-foreground` / `bg-foreground` — black
- `text-white` / `bg-white` / `bg-background` — white
- `text-accent` / `bg-accent` — green (#059669)
- `text-muted` — black with opacity (`rgba(0,0,0,0.6)`)
- `bg-surface` — near-white (`#fafafa`)
- Borders: `border-border` (black with opacity)

Never use: red, amber, yellow, orange, blue, purple, or any non-green/white/black color.

## Breakpoint

Custom breakpoint `framer:` at 810px. This is the only responsive breakpoint.

```
framer: "810px"  (replaces md/lg)
```

## Font

Inter via `next/font/google`. Stack: `Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif`

## Shadows

- Card: `shadow-[0_2px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)]`
- Hover: `shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)]`
- Elevated: `shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]`

## Component Conventions

- Use `Container` component for horizontal constraints (`max-w-container px-6 framer:px-10`)
- Use CSS variables from `globals.css`, mapped to Tailwind
- Use `clsx` + `tailwind-merge` for conditional classes
- Icons from `lucide-react` only
- No UI kit dependencies
